Context: George Brown College offers two primary Wi-Fi networks for its users: "Eduroam" and "GBC-Public." Eduroam is a premium Wi-Fi service for employees, faculty, and students, providing high-speed internet and access to internal college resources. It is also a global service, offering seamless internet connectivity in educational institutions worldwide. GBC-Public is for visitors and those who need only basic internet access, and it doesn't require authentication. The phone number for George Brown College is 416-415-2000, and the TTY number is 1-877-515-5559. The email address for inquiries is ask.george@georgebrown.ca. The information contained in the website is subject to change without notice.
